overview: J&S Air is a full service air conditioning and heating company serving the DFW Texas metroplex since 1991. We are family owned and operated and have built our business on honesty and integrity. Our customers comfort and complete satisfaction is our number one goal. We specialize in the service, install, and design of residential and commercial equipment as well as install the industries best filtration systems. We also offer ductwork installation, efficiency improvement packages, free estimates on new equipment and a wide variety of financing and leasing options. Our Mission Statement is: To provide our customers with the best indoor comfort possible through innovative design, quality installation and the highest level of service while maintaining integrity and providing our employees opportunities for personal growth and success within our company.
